{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_02_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ハロウィンイベント当日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、{user}さん\n何よ、この衣装は！？",
      "startTime": 4.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "資料に載っていたのと全然違うじゃない！？",
      "startTime": 6.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、デザイナーとイベント主催側の間で\n意思疎通がうまくいってなかったらしくて……",
      "startTime": 13.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ナースなのは分かってたけど\nこのコンセプトはなんなのよ！",
      "startTime": 18.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "もっとコスプレ感は抑えめだったはずでしょ！",
      "startTime": 21.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ゾンビでナースって……どんな世界観なのよ！\nこの子はどこで誰を看護してるの！？",
      "startTime": 28.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "め、冥界で……亡者を相手にかな？\n……たぶん",
      "startTime": 37.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "こんな変な格好で、ステージに立ったら\nかえってマイナスイメージがつくわ……",
      "startTime": 41.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "リーダーの私がこんな仕事をして\nLizNoirのファンが減ったらどうするのよ！",
      "startTime": 46.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、ポジティブに考えれば\n今までとは違うタイプのファンが増える可能性も……",
      "startTime": 51.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "どんなタイプのファンなのよ！　じゃあ貴方は\nこの格好をした私のファンになれるの！？",
      "startTime": 59.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……\nど、努力すれば……",
      "startTime": 63.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "努力しないと無理な時点で、ダメじゃない！",
      "startTime": 66.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……莉央さんの言う通りです。スタッフさんに話して\n違う仮装にしてもらうようにしましょう",
      "startTime": 73.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……やっぱり慣れない仕事を受けるのは――",
      "startTime": 75.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3866.6666666666742,
          "startTime": 79.73333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "メッセージだわ……誰かしら？\nえ？　愛とこころ？",
      "startTime": 84.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2766.6666666666656,
          "startTime": 84.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "『今日のイベント、こころと観に来てます\n莉央さんがどんな仮装をしてるのか楽しみです。愛』",
      "startTime": 90.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "『無難にカボチャの魔女とかだったらがっかりです！\n思い切り派手なの頼みますね。こころ』",
      "startTime": 98.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……ですって\nこの後輩達は、また私に余計なプレッシャーを……！",
      "startTime": 103.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はは、愛とこころらしいですね……",
      "startTime": 108.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "…………もぉ～～～～っ！\n分かったわよ！",
      "startTime": 116.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、待って！",
      "startTime": 118.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんですか？",
      "startTime": 120.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "…………衣装は変えないでいいわ\nゾンビのナース、OKよ",
      "startTime": 125.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……いいんですか？",
      "startTime": 127.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "後輩達が観に来ているのよ\n逃げる訳にはいかないわ",
      "startTime": 131.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "見事にやりきってあげるわよ\nどんな仮装をしても、私は私よ！",
      "startTime": 136.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "どんな格好でも、リズノワらしいステージにしてみせる\nよく考えたらこの程度の逆境、大したことじゃない",
      "startTime": 143.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_02_02-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "初めての海外で、四人で一からやりなおした\nあの経験に比べればね",
      "startTime": 152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_occult-01.m4a"
    },
    {
